'''Kthysh''' was a type of [[Vine/Legends|vine]] native to the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]]. Specially treated kthysh vines could be used to make strings for that could be used to manually load [[Bowcaster/Legends|bowcaster]]. Many warriors carried treated kthsyh vines in their [[Utility belt/Legends|utility pouches]] for emergencies.<ref name="EGWT">''[[The Essential Guide to Weapons and Technology]]''</ref>

[[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]] carried some kthysh vines in his [[Bandolier/Legends|bandolier]] pouch.

